data.description: ** Weekend showings only** Introducing a charming three-bedroom brick home with a modern touch. The updated kitchen boasts custom concrete countertops, complemented by laminate flooring throughout the main living spaces and bathroom. Enjoy the stunning mountain views from the great yard equipped with auto full sprinklers. The spacious backyard features a separate basement entrance, a covered patio, and RV parking. Plus, the potential to add a second bathroom downstairs, as it's already rough plumbed. Don't miss out on this lasting opportunity in a fantastic area at an attractive price point!
